## 5. Backend — API Gateway

### 5.1 Architecture Pattern

The API Gateway follows a strict **Controller → Service → Repository** layered architecture:

```
Routes (Express Router)
  ↓
Controllers (HTTP handling, validation, response formatting)
  ↓
Services (Business logic, orchestration, external calls)
  ↓
