## 11. Security & Data Integrity

### 11.1 Defense Layers

| Layer | Mechanism | Implementation |
|---|---|---|
| **HTTP Security** | Helmet.js | XSS, clickjacking, MIME sniffing protection |
| **CORS** | cors middleware | Origin whitelisting |
| **Input Validation** | Zod schemas | Type-safe validation on every POST endpoint |
| **Data Integrity** | SHA-256 hashing | Deterministic hash of metrics data |
| **Immutability** | Blockchain storage | Hash stored on Polygon L2 (cannot be altered) |
| **Access Control** | `onlyOwner` modifier | Only contract deployer can mint proofs |

### 11.2 Data Flow Security

```
Athlete submits metrics
  → Zod validates shape & types
    → Supabase stores raw data
      → AI computes composite score
        → SHA-256 hash generated
          → Hash stored on-chain
            → Anyone can verify: re-hash raw data, compare to on-chain hash
```

